      "text": "First, the top 3% who are actually building AI—the architects and builders creating foundational models—will be insanely well-paid. Second, quantum computing is the next frontier. The way computing works today will completely change with quantum. Everything we've written will need to be rewritten. Companies are already working on this, and there are over 100 startups in India working on quantum. Third, the future is about cross-disciplinary collaboration. AI will be integrated into every field—mechanical engineering, electrical engineering, biology, everything. The beautiful thing about computer science is that you can fit yourself into any industry."
    },
    {
